{"tid":602082,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"新手養魚，求教","createTime":"2018-03-22T17:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T14:14:48.000Z","uid":60140,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8e5371f92430618fb1381d060b9f1a2ec3aeff8f","tid":602082,"uid":60140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T17:43:40.000Z","msg":"啱啱開始養魚大概1個月多d，<br />\n第一條魚就係最易養既鬥魚，<br />\n由個水杯養，<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/d2c0bhyw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fd2c0bhyw&h=626a9135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再到養好水，換個盒仔養<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/e6tud10y\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fe6tud10y&h=febe2cb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到訂左個魚缸仔養，有齊基本野<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/s81lp6hj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fs81lp6hj&h=959e8add&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再之後，加埋燈魚及金青苔等混養<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1upkv5ab\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1upkv5ab&h=9e32b5b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊學邊嘗試，由於水太濁不停死魚又換水加藥劑，再到後來清走假景等，直到換成水草泥地，改善過濾等，希望可以改善水質<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/le8zt6um\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fle8zt6um&h=03e57646&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5ask3ufx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5ask3ufx&h=adcce038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾經我以為初初條鬥魚可以陪我走更遠既路，換哂野之後都仲好生猛，唔知點解呢兩日尾鰭爛左，身上多左白色野，唔知係傷痕定生病？ 最後仲走埋.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rdb0e53s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frdb0e53s&h=6fce8fe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dwko1by9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdwko1by9&h=e54ae1e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟係病左，定比其他魚咬？ <br />\n有冇識既人可以話我知，我個人懷疑係比金青苔咬傷致死，最近幾日加左2條金青苔（原本有2條），同4條白老鼠魚<br />\n<br />\n麻煩哂，好想知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7aad15b3c28ad6b31d83270b0df91b8e653d6e","tid":602082,"uid":11774,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:50:06.000Z","msg":"乜鬥魚可以同其他魚養埋一齊㗎咩？"},{"pid":"c5fbea9c17faeba5c3e4bdbd6e801eea114679a6","tid":602082,"uid":71343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:53:12.000Z","msg":"d水都仲白<br />\n水質未定就落魚實死啦<br />\n掉左個套缸佢重新開始啦"},{"pid":"59dfd952a6d04dc7f1d3e0372eff9ca63b5ffb46","tid":602082,"uid":51148,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:55:03.000Z","msg":"鬥魚唔駛咁<br />\n買酸葉啦"},{"pid":"821220aea4e6ffe230457b969410acf13250276b","tid":602082,"uid":9174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:56:48.000Z","msg":"養鬥魚唔洗搞咁多野 同埋唔可以混養 打撚死"},{"pid":"a905e3c22fa96694415ff164b82e199eab576f32","tid":602082,"uid":44646,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"7f7aad15b3c28ad6b31d83270b0df91b8e653d6e","tid":602082,"uid":11774,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:50:06.000Z","msg":"乜鬥魚可以同其他魚養埋一齊㗎咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:57:17.000Z","msg":"鬥魚係中國人<br />\n只會打自己人<br />\n(嚴格來講係打有長尾既魚)<br />\n<br />\n同燈魚一齊養都會怕到唔出來四圍遊"},{"pid":"4d3711cf2c67d011c38e73119fd7010d1de6ec67","tid":602082,"uid":44646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:58:20.000Z","msg":"金青苔係凶手<br />\n<br />\n另外，細缸無co2<br />\n種幾棵水榕算啦"},{"pid":"d319bd4b0547539e8316b12db2eb493afdff6153","tid":602082,"uid":145166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T05:59:17.000Z","msg":"去買d硝化菌，養好水先啦"},{"pid":"9ca99de20cc0e40e88f57dddaaf52c8cf6ed7b85","tid":602082,"uid":38103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T07:59:17.000Z","msg":"鬥魚唔洗養水，好粗養就得。<br />\n不過個缸唔好放其他野，同埋唔好放其他魚"},{"pid":"a7359681a374c9f80b46c053eefaa03761757b18","tid":602082,"uid":76793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:33:11.000Z","msg":"所有假景拎走<br />\n一係你泥太酸 燒尾<br />\n二黎你係咪加好多野落個缸到？<br />\n無可能咁白水 <br />\n我都養過 清水養已經ok<br />\n你用隔夜水"},{"pid":"40ba5d57b75108cb395df732b362a9fbc200b6f0","tid":602082,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T14:28:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"735d87ee34d85a5998579b6686964659ace1240d","tid":602082,"uid":145448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T06:20:35.000Z","msg":"一係水動盪,一係未落菌,你個缸換得咁密乜魚都死"},{"pid":"381cd5b51581f4a2623287fe614e6c4a20b175f3","tid":602082,"uid":60140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f7aad15b3c28ad6b31d83270b0df91b8e653d6e","tid":602082,"uid":11774,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:50:06.000Z","msg":"乜鬥魚可以同其他魚養埋一齊㗎咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T12:50:59.000Z","msg":"可以混養既，問過賣魚既，<br />\n唔好2條鬥魚放一齊就ok"},{"pid":"b345fc250abb1dcb37d1dc3a50d97136230a1f97","tid":602082,"uid":60140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d319bd4b0547539e8316b12db2eb493afdff6153","tid":602082,"uid":145166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T05:59:17.000Z","msg":"去買d硝化菌，養好水先啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T12:51:30.000Z","msg":"一直都有落，有加"},{"pid":"e9816d4cad22836419cd03cf120660aa755a5ffd","tid":602082,"uid":60140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"735d87ee34d85a5998579b6686964659ace1240d","tid":602082,"uid":145448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T06:20:35.000Z","msg":"一係水動盪,一係未落菌,你個缸換得咁密乜魚都死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T12:53:11.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打意見"},{"pid":"f3da3de5b26ac3e26f0bf0e716a325c911192f2a","tid":602082,"uid":60140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T12:59:09.000Z","msg":"多謝咁多位巴打意見，<br />\n自從鬥魚死左之後，<br />\n水質同魚都穩定左好多，<br />\n<br />\n水睇落乾淨左好多，<br />\n同埋已經一星期無死過任何魚仔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nhit83uv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnhit83uv&h=8aaa5d10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/klo7gn9x\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fklo7gn9x&h=3e4fada0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，第一條魚就咁無左總有d失落 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3031602fd395f5d93635e2ff620d5d9415cd1e02","tid":602082,"uid":145166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b345fc250abb1dcb37d1dc3a50d97136230a1f97","tid":602082,"uid":60140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d319bd4b0547539e8316b12db2eb493afdff6153","tid":602082,"uid":145166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T05:59:17.000Z","msg":"去買d硝化菌，養好水先啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T12:51:30.000Z","msg":"一直都有落，有加"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:00:21.000Z","msg":"我係上下奇買日本粒狀嗰隻，感覺唔錯"},{"pid":"0df8fa80194bf0dccafca00c2aca252c2146622b","tid":602082,"uid":60140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:00:54.000Z","msg":"鬥魚死左之後只換過一次水，<br />\n落過2次硝化細菌，<br />\n同1次水質澄清劑"},{"pid":"89b805699f3100fe503a3018bbbc3fe74d9cffb9","tid":602082,"uid":60140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3031602fd395f5d93635e2ff620d5d9415cd1e02","tid":602082,"uid":145166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b345fc250abb1dcb37d1dc3a50d97136230a1f97","tid":602082,"uid":60140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d319bd4b0547539e8316b12db2eb493afdff6153","tid":602082,"uid":145166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T05:59:17.000Z","msg":"去買d硝化菌，養好水先啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T12:51:30.000Z","msg":"一直都有落，有加"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:00:21.000Z","msg":"我係上下奇買日本粒狀嗰隻，感覺唔錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:02:24.000Z","msg":"我係用淘寶淘果set缸連配件連埋，<br />\n用住先，<br />\n我諗效果還可以"},{"pid":"14218520cc9fa8d52e57d5085ad274ebbf0a84d3","tid":602082,"uid":141871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:07:35.000Z","msg":"鬥魚就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你越對佢好，比越多設備佢，就會死比你睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而細細個玻璃兜養住，除左食乜都唔需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就可以長命百歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n養過幾十條半月、巨鬥將軍都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d065b758eb9c02bebdfc998821f4ca362ac8ed08","tid":602082,"uid":60140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7359681a374c9f80b46c053eefaa03761757b18","tid":602082,"uid":76793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:33:11.000Z","msg":"所有假景拎走<br />\n一係你泥太酸 燒尾<br />\n二黎你係咪加好多野落個缸到？<br />\n無可能咁白水 <br />\n我都養過 清水養已經ok<br />\n你用隔夜水"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:09:58.000Z","msg":"咩叫燒尾？<br />\n一直水唔清就隔幾日加硝化細菌同水質澄清劑咁啦<br />\n<br />\n之前養落得金清苔2條，<br />\n假景太多「攝」住好多魚糧，<br />\n浸耐左再發左，<br />\n就搞到水質好差<br />\n<br />\n所以後尾清哂所有假景，<br />\n換泥地，<br />\n重新換過濾果d，<br />\n不過因為大部份舊水所以仲未變清<br />\n而家過左一星期清返"},{"pid":"be80a0879bf548ba629cebf5d9e036c0042ffe5d","tid":602082,"uid":60140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14218520cc9fa8d52e57d5085ad274ebbf0a84d3","tid":602082,"uid":141871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:07:35.000Z","msg":"鬥魚就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你越對佢好，比越多設備佢，就會死比你睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而細細個玻璃兜養住，除左食乜都唔需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就可以長命百歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n養過幾十條半月、巨鬥將軍都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:10:40.000Z","msg":"唉，好似失戀咁feel"},{"pid":"ab282298cd5c9ab23170af19ea34c4a53c359b0f","tid":602082,"uid":47967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0df8fa80194bf0dccafca00c2aca252c2146622b","tid":602082,"uid":60140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:00:54.000Z","msg":"鬥魚死左之後只換過一次水，<br />\n落過2次硝化細菌，<br />\n同1次水質澄清劑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:14:42.000Z","msg":"個setting好<br />\n落左硝化細菌養好菌連清水劑都唔洗用"},{"pid":"6ee8cf2de9f207be11f9c71ca79518e1707c5258","tid":602082,"uid":60140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:17:58.000Z","msg":"而家個缸有4條金清苔，同4條白鼠<br />\n基本上會清哂d餘糧，青苔果d<br />\n好似因為咁而水質保持到<br />\n<br />\n黎緊想再追加買返包燈魚加落去"},{"pid":"a225ce28af8ea963768c96ab6de9e5fb41227c61","tid":602082,"uid":170015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d065b758eb9c02bebdfc998821f4ca362ac8ed08","tid":602082,"uid":60140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7359681a374c9f80b46c053eefaa03761757b18","tid":602082,"uid":76793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:33:11.000Z","msg":"所有假景拎走<br />\n一係你泥太酸 燒尾<br />\n二黎你係咪加好多野落個缸到？<br />\n無可能咁白水 <br />\n我都養過 清水養已經ok<br />\n你用隔夜水"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:09:58.000Z","msg":"咩叫燒尾？<br />\n一直水唔清就隔幾日加硝化細菌同水質澄清劑咁啦<br />\n<br />\n之前養落得金清苔2條，<br />\n假景太多「攝」住好多魚糧，<br />\n浸耐左再發左，<br />\n就搞到水質好差<br />\n<br />\n所以後尾清哂所有假景，<br />\n換泥地，<br />\n重新換過濾果d，<br />\n不過因為大部份舊水所以仲未變清<br />\n而家過左一星期清返"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:20:23.000Z","msg":"燒尾，有啲魚例如孔雀魚，PH 值唔岩條尾<br />\n會慢慢爛<br />\n<br />\n你唔再種水草就拎走啲泥，泥會令水變酸"}]}